        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockInputCell>











      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Now that we have a token, we create a client, for this we need to have the <code>huggingface_hub</code> library installed, which we do using conda or pip</p>
